      "description": "Offering an impeccable 997.1 Carrera S, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the 3.8L M97 flat-six and a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle. This example exhibits zero bore scoring and has been proactively fitted with an LN Engineering IMS Solution. The PASM-equipped chassis remains taut, delivering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback via the hydraulic rack. Finished in concours-level paint with a flawless interior, this 911 retains its factory-spec compression and linear torque delivery. A mechanically superlative specimen for the discerning collector.",
